/**************************************************************
 *      
 * FUNCTION:        MSG_MAIL_COMPOSER_SEND_MESSAGE_LATER
 * PASS:            none
 * RETURN:          none
 * DESCRIPTION:
 *         Compose a message from the UI and send it later
 *
 * REVISION HISTORY:
